name: JenaTesting168
description:
Jena 175 minus:
3 meanings with insurmountable uncertainties as to deep Indo-European coding:
* cut
* guts
* scratch
2 meanings with widespread uncertainties, difficulties and loanwords across several branches of Indo-European:
* person
* walk
2 meanings problematic, especially in Germanic:  
* hot (vis à vis warm, the heiss/warm roots)
* run (vis à vis walk, the rennen/laufen roots)
